<HEADLINE>
<P>
TORTURE VICTIM 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 I was very upset about the article on the transient who was tortured to death 
at the 1800 block of Wilcox Avenue in Hollywood (Nov. 30). 
</P>
<P>
 Robert Lee Bryant, the victim, was my brother.He hung with all the black 
dudes, his two last girlfriends were Mexican (one of them still very much in 
love with him), so whoever said that he was touting white supremacy was a liar! 
Robert's best friends were all black and Mexican and they are outraged about 
that article, and so am I. 
</P>
<P>
 My brother did have a home here with me and my mother. He had just gotten out 
of Wayside Nov. 25. He would have come back home, if he had the chance. 
</P>
<P>
 DEBBIE BRYANT 
</P>
<P>
 Tujunga 
