<HEADLINE>
<P>
O.C. QUIZ 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Multiple choice: Who cost Orange County the most this year? Pick one: a) 
illegal, non-English-speaking nannies, b) pregnant teen-age girls, (c) greedy 
white men. 
</P>
<P>
 JAMES P. SULLIVAN 
</P>
<P>
 Reseda 
</P>
</TEXT>
