senior vice president of Smart & Final. In his new role, Griffin, 54, will 
oversee two broad-line food service distribution companies.With his promotion 
to executive vice president, Griffin continues his responsibility for buying, 
merchandising, distribution and information systems for Smart & Final stores. 
Los Angeles-based Smart & Final operates 147 no-membership warehouse grocery 
stores. 
</P>
