 * Scott Bowman, president and chief executive of San Francisco-based I. Magnin 
department stores, has decided to leave the company after the chain's 
operations are phased out early next year. R.H. Macy & Co. recently decided to 
discontinue its I. Magnin operations. I. Magnin is now liquidating its 
inventory and will close some time in January. The New York-based Macy and the 
Cincinnati-based Federated Department Stores complete a merger today. 
</P>
