Inc., a Santa Ana wholesale distributor of microcomputer products. He will 
remain president of its subsidiary, Ingram Micro Inc. Canada. Elchesen became 
president and chief operating officer of Ingram Micro Inc. Canada after the 
merger of Ingram Computer and Micro D in 1989. 
</P>
