<TEXT>
<P>
 Residents' opinions will be sought at a workshop on the development of a 
master plan for the city's transportation center. 
</P>
<P>
 The master plan focuses on the 60-acre zone around the downtown transportation 
center. Three proposed alternatives for the zone will be discussed at the 
workshop, which is the third in a series of four. 
</P>
<P>
 The workshop will be at 7 p.m. on Jan. 12 at the Fullerton Main Library, 353 
W. Commonwealth Ave.MIMI KO 
